text:
In this task you will be required to identify what color the letters of the word presented are.

To do this you'll need to respond with the following keys:

Press {{key_1}} if the letters are {{color_1}}
Press {{key_2}} if the letters are {{color_2}}
Press {{key_3}} if the letters are {{color_3}}
Press {{key_4}} if the letters are {{color_4}}
